The full dataset may be used to understand:

- schema
- date coverage
- variable definitions
- number of brands and markets
- missingness structure
- potential anomalies
- general target distribution
- data-quality concerns

### Training-Only Model EDA

Training data should determine:

- transformation choice
- useful lags
- useful rolling windows
- feature selection
- imputation methods
- feature scaling
- encoding rules
- outlier treatment

For rolling validation, these decisions should ideally be re-estimated within each fold.

